{"title":"罗布泊的骆驼","authors":["马畏安"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":3,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗布泊的骆驼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马畏安"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远远地望见了你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫漫黄沙中的一点驼色"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看清了你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那熟悉的驼峰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那高大的躯体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稀疏的毛发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粗糙的皮肤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包裹着坚强的骨骼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一束骆驼刺举了起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怯怯地凑近你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艺术家给你奉上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人类善心的一点寄托"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你却昂首天外"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圆瞪双眼纵声吼叫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"送到嘴边的食物"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你从未见过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也从未吃过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许你要奔跑十里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能喝一口水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许你要寻觅百里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能吃一口红柳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的生活"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从来就这般落寞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既有你，当然就有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你子女的子女的子女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既有你，必然也会有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你父母的父母的父母"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世世代代，生生不息"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样奔波"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样拚搏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在沙漠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少严寒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少酷热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风沙的抽打"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰雪的折磨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"造就你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚韧、剽悍、顽强"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又粗豪的性格"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论你父母一生下你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论你一生下你的爱子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就将柔弱的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"托付给无际的沙漠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狂风呼啸飞沙走石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你听来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是和谐的音乐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白骨被戈壁埋没"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗布泊的野骆驼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是沙漠之魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是生命之歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看见你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我才悟出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上只有沙漠般的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却没有没有生命的沙漠"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}